    "body" : "<p>For me this error was due to the reason <strong>Gradle</strong> as installed as <strong>sudo</strong> and I was trying as default user to run Gradle.</p>\n\n<p>Try:</p>\n\n<pre><code>sudo gradle -version\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>or</p>\n\n<pre><code>sudo gradle -v\n</code></pre>\n"
