    "answer_id" : 30276458,
    "question_id" : 22307516,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>I had a problem with this too. It said wrong directory when it was correct. So I just created a local variable with the name of JAVA_HOME omitting the final /bin/java. It worked fine for me.</p>\n"
  }, {
    "comments" : [ {
      "owner" : {
        "account_id" : 2543399,
