    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>Adding below lines in build.gradle solved my issue .</p>\n\n<pre><code>sourceCompatibility = JavaVersion.VERSION_1_8\ntargetCompatibility = JavaVersion.VERSION_1_8\n</code></pre>\n"
