    "is_accepted" : false,
    "score" : 0,
    "last_activity_date" : 1734695860,
    "creation_date" : 1734695860,
    "answer_id" : 79297157,
    "question_id" : 22307516,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>I had the same error and what solved it for me was removing the <code>/bin</code> part from the end of the <code>JAVA_HOME</code> path. Now the variable points to the whole java directory.</p>\n"
  } ],
